data.description: This charming well maintained downtown historic home is conveniently located in Morristown, TN. This home offers over 2,500 square feet of finished living space with a blend of timeless architecture and contemporary updates. Step inside to be greeted by lovely natural light, tons of character, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. This spacious home features 3 large bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and large laundry room providing ample space for all. This home also comes with a remodeled kitchen which creates even more space to live and entertain. Other features include fireplaces that grace various rooms throughout the house, a second level sunroom which could provide a tranquil place, ideal for reading, morning coffee, or simply enjoying the views. The property spans almost half an acre with newly planted willow trees creating a lovely place to call home. Outside you'll find an amazing and picturesque wrap-around porch, two large outbuildings, with plenty of space for storage or working on hobbies. With a back deck perfect for entertaining, you'll enjoy cherished moments with family and friends. All of this and under an hour from Knoxville, Sevierville, Pigeon Forge and Gatlinburg!! Come and check this one out today and make it your new place to call home! Buyer to verify all information herein.
